instructions: put the plate on the charger
put the napkin on the plate
put the dinner fork left of the charger
put the salad fork left of the dinner fork
put the dinner knife right of the charger with the blade to the left
put the tea spoon right of the dinner knife
put the soup spoon to the right of the tea spoon
put the water glass at one o'clock to the charger
put the wine glass to the right of the water glass
put the wine glass under the wine glass
put the coffee cup at 2 o'clock to the soup spoon
put the bread plate at 11 o'clock of the charger
put the butter knife on the bread plate pointed right
put the dessert fork at 12 o'clock of the charger, tines to the right
put the dessert spoon underneath the dessert fork facing left
